requirements.text:
In the `initializeSeedData` function in `backend/main.mo`, update Dave Clarke's 9 event records to exactly match the following verified details (all retain sourceLabel 'RA' and eventUrl 'https://ra.co'):
(1) eventTitle 'Live Techno Experience with Dave Clarke' — venue 'TBA (Industrial 236 Warehouse / Vantek Warehouse)', Vancouver, Canada, Fri 6 Mar 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-03-06T22:00:00Z';
(2) eventTitle 'Dave Clarke in Toronto' — venue '821 Runnymede Rd (or 131 McCormack St)', Toronto, Canada, Sat 7 Mar 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-03-07T22:00:00Z';
(3) eventTitle 'WONDER RAVE' — venue 'TBA East', Nancy, France, Fri 13 Mar 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-03-13T22:00:00Z';
(4) eventTitle 'OFF THE GRID: Elli Acula, RISA TANAGUSHI, Dave Clarke' — venue 'Mia Mao', Paris, France, Sat 14 Mar 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-03-14T22:00:00Z';
(5) eventTitle 'fabric: Palms Trax, Sedef Adasï, Alex Kassian, Dave Clarke, Setaoc Mass, Michelle Manetti, FAFF' — venue 'fabric', London, UK, Sat 4 Apr 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-04-04T22:00:00Z';
(6) eventTitle 'City Wall x Dave Clarke' — venue 'Concorde 2', Brighton, UK, Fri 15 May 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-05-15T22:00:00Z';
(7) eventTitle 'Ostend Beach Festival 2026' — venue 'Klein Strand', Ostend, Belgium, Fri 10 Jul 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-07-10T18:00:00Z';
(8) eventTitle 'Luvmuzik presents Dave Clarke & Gary Beck' — venue 'District Cardiff', Cardiff, UK, Fri 24 Jul 2026, dateTime ISO '2026-07-24T22:00:00Z';
(9) eventTitle 'Iceland Eclipse' — venue 'Hellissandur', Hellissandur, Iceland, Thu 12 Aug 2027, dateTime ISO '2027-08-12T20:00:00Z'.
All 9 events must be associated with Dave Clarke's artist ID. All other artist event datasets (Jeff Mills 16 events, Richie Hawtin 1 event, Joey Beltram, Derrick May, Juan Atkins, Kevin Saunderson, Robert Hood) must remain unchanged. The `postupgrade` system hook must continue to call `initializeSeedData` unconditionally. After deploy, `getEventsByArtist` queried with Dave Clarke's artist ID must return all 9 events with the correct venue strings and dateTimes.
